Start

Tell the user the purpose "I will tell them what to do considering the day of the week"

Ask user for the current day of the week

Day gets stored in a variable called Day

if day Monday
print Start your week with a workout

elif day Tuesday
print It's a great day to read a book

elif day Wednesday
print Mid-week movie night!

elif day Thursday
    print Try a new recipe

elif day Friday
print Relax and enjoy the weekend

elif day Saturday
print Go for a hike!

elif day Sunday
print Take it easy and prepare for the week ahead!

else:
print Invalid input! Please enter a valid day of the week.